---
title: Salisbury Beyond Meat® in Onion Gravy with Creamy Sweet Potato Mash and Roasted Broccoli
description: We're bringing back memories of grandma's kitchen with these retro Beyond Meat® patties smothered in onion gravy. Creamy mashed sweet potatoes alongside are a must, while roasted broccoli finishes off the plate with a green touch.
